description: Complete mesh catalog for the ModularSciFi asset pack. Paths are ready for spawn_static_mesh_actor. Bounds are null until measured via measure_bounds.py.

category_descriptions.modular_building: Grid-snapping structural pieces (500cm). Walls, floors, roofs, corners, windows, doors.
category_descriptions.compound_module: Pre-built room modules (LivingModules, MainStation). Always paired with indoor variant at same transform.
category_descriptions.connector: Bridge and roof connectors that join compound modules together.
category_descriptions.interior: Indoor detail pieces: partitions, columns, indoor windows, furniture.
category_descriptions.terrain: Cliffs, rocks, dirt, minerals. Use random scale (0.5-6x) and full 3-axis rotation.
category_descriptions.vegetation: Grass and plants. Scatter with random scale/rotation.
category_descriptions.infrastructure: Fences, pillars, poles, platforms, supports. Often placed along paths/perimeters.
category_descriptions.prop: Small objects: barrels, boxes, lamps, terminals, pumps. Cluster near structures.
category_descriptions.panel: Flat structural detail surfaces. Used at arbitrary rotations for wall/floor detail.
category_descriptions.tubes: Piping system with 23 variants for complex routing.
category_descriptions.door: Standalone door and frame meshes (not modular grid doors).
category_descriptions.decal: Flat planes for projected surface detail.
